The paper discusses a technique for enhancing the effectiveness of information retrieval, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of Wikipedia and WordNet as data sources suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-categories of Natural Language Processing (cs.CL), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.DL).
